Package: pfem
Type: Package
Title: Particle Filter EM Algorithm for Hidden Markov Models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Russell G. Almond
Maintainer: Russell Almond <ralmond@fsu.edu>
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Russell",
           family = "Almond",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "ralmond@fsu.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8876-9337"))
Description: Provides a framework for describing Hidden Markov Models
	     for panel data (multiple individuals, limited measurement
	     occasions).  Can simulate data from the models, produce
	     smoothed estimates of latent variable trajectories using
	     particle filter, and combines particle filter and EM
	     algorithm to produce parameter estimates.
License: MIT License
URL: http://ralmond.net/pfem
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    methods, parallel, R6,
    R (>= 4.4.0)
Imports: stats, utils, rlang
Suggests: 
    ggplot2,
    plotly,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    tidyverse,
    cowplot,
    vdiffr,
    withr,
    kableExtra,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
